    "description": "ーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー<br>The game was created by Byking Inc.<br><br>This work is a game produced by Byking Inc. for newcomer training.<br>It may not work properly depending on your PC environment.<br>Also, unintentional glitches may occur in the game.<br>Please understand.<br><br>The game cannot be played using a controller.<br>Keyboard and mouse operation is required for the playing environment.<br>Please understand this in advance.<br><br><br>The game cannot be played using a controller.<br><br>ーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー<br><br><br>ABOUT THE GAME<br>&quot;ORDER9&quot; is an &quot;auto-battle card game&quot; where players choose a character, and help lead them to victory over other opponents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/834aac3979987cbdcea3c5867e3c2285.poster.avif?t=1763467269\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/834aac3979987cbdcea3c5867e3c2285.webm?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/834aac3979987cbdcea3c5867e3c2285.mp4?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CHARACTER SELECTION<br>Choose 1 from 9 available characters.<br>From the remaining, 3 opponents will be randomly chosen to fight you in battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/6cc230e8db9b5f829cdd855ccb3cc7a3.poster.avif?t=1763467269\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/6cc230e8db9b5f829cdd855ccb3cc7a3.webm?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/6cc230e8db9b5f829cdd855ccb3cc7a3.mp4?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CHARACTER ABILITIES<br>Every character has 3 abilities, &quot;skill&quot;, &quot;buff&quot; and &quot;punch&quot;.<br>An ability will be chosen at random each turn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/de54377ce4b53e815dd975a6aebf85d0.poster.avif?t=1763467269\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/de54377ce4b53e815dd975a6aebf85d0.webm?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/de54377ce4b53e815dd975a6aebf85d0.mp4?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>FLOW OF COMBAT<br>Combat plays out in 3 phases: The &quot;Target Phase&quot;, &quot;Choice Phase&quot;, and &quot;Battle Phase&quot;.<br><br>- Target Phase:<br>The 4 participants will automatically determine their target(s) for the turn, influenced by their abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/0907370c76dad443faa14cc489f3ca5c.avif?t=1763467269\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br>- Choice Phase:<br>By using &quot;mana&quot;, the player can choose cards to change the conditions of battle.<br>Aim to give your character the upper hand!<br>e.g. Increasing everyone's defense when your character is being targeted the most..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/37ccfe1325c23175efff1a0d0a7bf325.poster.avif?t=1763467269\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/37ccfe1325c23175efff1a0d0a7bf325.webm?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/37ccfe1325c23175efff1a0d0a7bf325.mp4?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Battle Phase:<br>All characters will perform their actions for the turn automatically, influenced by their abilities in the Target Phase, and the player's actions in the Choice Phase.<br>Turns continue in this way until an ultimate victor is determined.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/fcc68e3efe03b56b35575034fd3753f9.poster.avif?t=1763467269\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/fcc68e3efe03b56b35575034fd3753f9.webm?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046500/extras/fcc68e3efe03b56b35575034fd3753f9.mp4?t=1763467269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Control the game! Control the battle!<br>Lead your chosen one to victory!!",
